So apparently I still have access to this. Hi people's! The good news is. I'm back to being hyper since surgery.
Always try to be kind, and compassionate. Be patient and loving. You never know what kind of strength you can give someone.
So I hope that if you can take one thing from this...
What may be painful to one person may be nothing to someone else, but that doesn't diminish the pain, that doesn't take away it's real ness.
And my situation isn't even as bad as others have had it. Every body has a sad story they can tell you.
I can't wait to have way too much energy, be a weirdo, enjoy every thing again. I can't wait to have myself back.
